CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778817908
OL,3,CCheapest supermarket for branded items
OL,4,Crevealed
OL,6,FAsda has been named the cheapest
OL,7,Fsupermarket for branded groceries for
OL,8,Fthe third consecutive month, with its
OL,9,Fstandard prices even beating loyalty
OL,10,Fcard deals at Tesco and Sainsbury's,
OL,11,FWhich? has found.
OL,13,FFor those not using a loyalty card,
OL,14,FWhich? found that 240 branded items at
OL,15,FSainsbury's were 17% more expensive
OL,16,Fthan Asda ` which does not offer
OL,17,Fexclusive prices to Asda Rewards
OL,18,Fcustomers ` while Tesco (#912.56) was
OL,19,F15% more.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
