FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778817908
OL,3,CCheapest supermarket for branded items
OL,4,Crevealed
OL,6,FAll 240 items, which included Dolmio
OL,7,FBolognese Sauce, Nescafe Azera instant
OL,8,Fcoffee and Mr Kipling Angel Cake
OL,9,FSlices, cost #795.21 at Asda.
OL,11,FThis also meant that for the third
OL,12,Fmonth in a row, the UK's two biggest
OL,13,Fsupermarkets were more expensive than
OL,14,FWaitrose on branded items (#895.28)
OL,15,Ffor shoppers who do not have a loyalty
OL,16,Fcard.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
