OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778817908
OL,3,CCheapest supermarket for branded items
OL,4,Crevealed
OL,6,FThe largest difference in average
OL,7,Fprice in April was Colgate Plax Cool
OL,8,FMint Mouthwash 500ml which cost #2 at
OL,9,FAsda but #4.50 at both Tesco and
OL,10,FSainsbury's without a loyalty card ` a
OL,11,Fdifference of 125%.
OL,13,FIn another example, a 50-pack of
OL,14,FPampers Premium Protection New Baby
OL,15,FDiapers cost #4.54 with a Tesco
OL,16,FClubcard but #8.70 for those without `
OL,17,Fa 92% difference.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
