PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778817908
OL,3,CCheapest supermarket for branded items
OL,4,Crevealed
OL,6,FThese prices ` which were available to
OL,7,Fall shoppers ` were even cheaper than
OL,8,Fthe member-only prices at both Tesco
OL,9,Fwith a Clubcard by 3% (#821.67) and
OL,10,FSainsbury's with a Nectar card by 6%
OL,11,F(#850.39).
OL,13,FMorrisons was 5% more expensive than
OL,14,FAsda on average when using a More card
OL,15,F(#838.15), and 6% more costly without
OL,16,Fone (#839.18).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
