OL,3,CCheapest supermarket for branded items
OL,4,Crevealed
OL,6,FWhich? found Waitrose to be the
OL,7,Fcheapest for several of the products
OL,8,Fincluded in the analysis, including
OL,9,FDolmio Bolognese Sauce Onion And
OL,10,FGarlic 450g, which was #1.50 on
OL,11,Faverage in Waitrose compared with
OL,12,F#2.60 at most other supermarkets,
OL,13,Fincluding Morrisons, Sainsbury's and
OL,14,FTesco for those without a loyalty card
OL,15,F` a difference of 73%.
OL,17,FWhich? found Sharwood's Medium Egg
OL,18,FNoodles 226g was #1.36 at Waitrose but
OL,19,F#2.10 in Tesco for non-members ` a
OL,20,Fdifference of 54%.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
