PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778817908
OL,3,CCheapest supermarket for branded items
OL,4,Crevealed
OL,6,FAldi and Lidl are not included in the
OL,7,Fanalysis because they do not stock a
OL,8,Fsufficiently wide range of branded
OL,9,Fgroceries.
OL,11,FWhich? retail editor Reena Sewraz
OL,12,Fsaid: "Our latest analysis shows Asda
OL,13,Fcontinues to offer the lowest prices
OL,14,Fon branded groceries without shoppers
OL,15,Fneeding a loyalty card.
OL,17,F"At the same time, the gap between the
OL,18,Fcheapest and most expensive
OL,19,Fsupermarkets is growing, with some
OL,20,Fshoppers paying up to 17% more for the
OL,21,Fsame basket.
