OL,3,CCheapest supermarket for branded items
OL,4,Crevealed
OL,6,F"In some cases, consumers are paying
OL,7,Fdouble for identical products
OL,8,Fdepending on where they shop and
OL,9,Fwhether they have a loyalty card."
OL,11,FA Sainsbury's spokesman said: "All
OL,12,Fexamples in this report were cheaper
OL,13,Fon Nectar Prices and our customers
OL,14,Fknow a good deal when they see one,
OL,15,Fwith 85% of sales involving a Nectar
OL,16,Fcard.
